snippet.title: How to Play Arimaa (full version)
snippet.description:
You can play this game online at http://arimaa.com/  Arimaa is a fun and simple board game, which has a very deep strategy! Learn to play in just a few minutes.

To learn more about Arimaa see: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arimaa
